title: Angeline's Bakery and Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Bakery, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Cozy little bakery and cafe that offers a number of raw specials and gluten-free vegan treats. Offers bagels, scones, salads, wraps, and the baked goods are clearly marked which ones are vegan. Also carries a wide variety of milk alternatives such as hemp, soy, rice, and almond milk.
